'''泡螺属'''（学名：{{lang|la|''Hydatina''}}）为[[腹足綱|腹足綱]]的一個[[海螺|海螺]]的[[属_(生物)|属]]。原屬[[後鰓目|後鰓目]]或[[頭楯目|頭楯目]]（Cephalaspidea）的[[泡螺科|泡螺科]]，今屬[[異鰓類|異鰓類]][[下異鰓類|下異鰓類]]支序的[[捻螺總科|捻螺總科]][[船尾螺科|船尾螺科]]。

==物種==
本屬物種計有：
* [[白带泡螺|白带泡螺]]（''[[Hydatina_albocincta|Hydatina albocincta]]'' <small>Van der Hoeven, 1839</small>）：又稱[[三带泡螺|三带泡螺]]
* ''[[Hydatina_cinctoria|Hydatina cinctoria]]'' {{small|Perry, 1811}}：分佈於[[南非|南非]]；也有意見認為本物種是[[黑带泡螺|黑带泡螺]]的異名，只是兩個物種的顏色有所不同。
* [[精美泡螺|精美泡螺]] ''[[Hydatina_exquisita|Hydatina exquisita]]'' Voskuil, 1995
* ''[[Hydatina_montilai|Hydatina montilai]]'' <small>Delsaerdt, 1996</small>: Distribution: Philippines.
* [[泡螺|泡螺]] ''[[Hydatina_physis|Hydatina physis]]'' <small>([[Carolus_Linnaeus|Linnaeus]], 1758)</small>
* ''[[Hydatina_velum|Hydatina velum]]'' <small>[[Johann_Friedrich_Gmelin|Gmelin]], 1791</small> (probably color variant and synonym of ''Hydatina zonata'')
** Distribution: Indian Ocean, East Africa
** Length: 25–50 mm
* ''[[Hydatina_vesicaria|Hydatina vesicaria]]'' <small>(Lightfoot, 1786)</small> '''brown-lined paper bubble'''
** Distribution: Florida, Mexico, Caribbean.
** Length: 17–45 mm
** Description: lives on the bottom at the depth of 8 m to 64 m; very fragile and delicate shell with fine brown spiral lines
* [[黑带泡螺|黑带泡螺]] ''[[Hydatina_zonata|Hydatina zonata]]'' {{small|[[Daniel_Solander|Solander]] in Lightfoot, 1786}}
;異名：
* [[玫瑰泡螺|玫瑰泡螺]]（''[[Hydatina_amplustre|Hydatina amplustre]]'' <small>[[Carolus_Linnaeus|Linnaeus]], 1758</small>）：今屬[[飾紋螺屬|飾紋螺屬]]。

==寄生蟲==
1964年在[[馬拉維湖|馬拉維湖]]的{{link-en|猴子灣|Monkey Bay}}（Monkey Bay）發現的一種泡螺屬物種被一種[[血吸蟲|血吸蟲]]的幼體[[寄生|寄生]]{{r|Wright 1967}}。

